---
title: Pesto Mozzarella Piadina with Roasted Zucchini and Sweet Bell Pepper
description: This meal captures everything we love about the warm weather! Our piadina is a bit messy to eat, but worth it, because it's loaded with colourful zucchini, stringy mozzarella and creamy pesto. What more could you want?
